name: Nirvana
description:
The light all depends on the way things are illuminated, it depends on the situations, on everything that surrounds us. An instant in which I felt connected with the energies of my friends, a place to which we wanted to travel, from the body, the energy, to nirvana.

This was one of those moments in which the dance embraced me, he told me that this was the way. Here he participated with the first professional company "Cuerpo Rojo" Contemporary Dance. A great journey of movement, friends and experiences.
